    "The last section of the CRF contains a segment specifically for the DFU expert clinician to diagnose the current healing phase for each wound to the best of their abilities and to provide a confidence level percentage for their classification only for research purposes.To maintain consistency in the dataset, for many categories, suggested picks for the patient and clinicians are provided in the CRF.",
